h2o-rpm
---------
A set of scripts to package h2o into an rpm. Skeleton borrowed from orientdb3-rpm which does the same thing.

Setup
-----
    $ yum groupinstall "Development Tools"

Building
--------
    $ make rpm H2O_VERSION="3.26.0" H2O_RELEASE="4765"


Resulting RPM will be avaliable at $(shell pwd)

Installing and operating
------------------------
    $ sudo yum install h2o*.rpm

Libs, binaries, configs and logs are in /opt/h2o.

